  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Investment by CDC into RBL Bank Limited to provide support to the bank to expand it&apos;s operations into India&apos;s poorer states where current access to financial services is limited. Our investment will help RBL Bank to reach more customers and boost the level of financing available to SMEs and agribusiness in the country. In particular, to open up lending to small-scale farmers and female micro-entrepreneurs, who have previously been excluded from formal financial services.</narrative>
  </description>
